::Prowl::

Prowl nods. The plan was good, but chances were, the Alliance would still 
discover their presence either way. He looks back at Dinobot.

"Allright," he says, taking out his claw weapon and grabbing it tightly, 
"We'll have a bit of trouble for the escape though. Those doors can't be 
opened without clearence, something we don't have."

He reaches into his storage compartment, closing his hand over something 
extra he had taken from the night vision bin of the Cybertronian Fire's 
storage.

"If we meet any Alliance members on our way out, don't slag 'em, and let me 
do the talking. I have a plan to get us out."

With that, he silently moves the vent cover aside, jumping down to the floor 
without making a sound. He heads toward Nemesis, careful not to step on 
anything.
